full_text: The Current State Of Telehealth Evidence: A Rapid Review | Health Affairs https://t.co/ufBwGGajOZ #telehealth #telemedicine https://t.co/6bCeOyEe6o

A recent study shows that telehealth outcomes are roughly equivalent to those from in-person care. Does your company use telehealth to offer convenient care to employees? #healthcare #healthpolicy https://t.co/oxLhzueOdm

It is comforting to see such consistent findings for treating mental health conditions.  Most of the studies in this meta-study found similar outcomes in-person and through tele-medicine. https://t.co/GNmfpUlXqU
